dc:description: Green glass.  Intact.  Very bubbly.  Sandy and black impurities.  Milky weathering.  Rim horizontally outsplayed, folded upward and inward and flattened on top.  Cylindrical neck.  Solid body with no distinct shape.  Flat base with pontil mark.  Hollow part of  vessel narrow with downward taper.  Body and rim are uneven.
